If all the above validations have passed, set the return code to 3 "Replying router is an egress for the FEC at stack-depth <RSC>".
Set the FEC-Status to 1 and return.
}
Else, if the Label-stack-depth is 1 and the Target FEC Stack sub-TLV at FEC-stack-depth is 53 (SR Candidate Path Associated PSID - IPv6 sub-TLV), {
